sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Client
  participant R as Route/Controller
  participant V as Zod Validation
  participant U as Use Case
  participant P as Permission Policy
  participant Repo as Repository
  participant DB as Database

  C->>R: HTTP Request
  R->>V: Validate body/query/path
  V-->>R: Typed input
  R->>U: input + AuthContext
  U->>P: Require permission
  U->>Repo: Query/mutate with tenant boundary
  Repo->>DB: Parameterized query
  DB-->>Repo: Rows
  Repo-->>U: Domain/Application model
  U-->>R: Result
  R-->>C: Serialized API response
